    "Figure 4 shows the number of articles published per year.",
    "We identified 52 relevant conference articles and 16 relevant journal articles.",
    "Nine relevant documents came from books, reports, and workshops.",
    "More than half of the articles (52%) came from the International Requirements Engineering Conference (RE) and 16% from Traceability in Emerging Forms of Software Engineering (TEFSE).",
